    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Provide technical and financial support to MoWCSW and MOHA on the crime against women database along with other UN agencies\r\n\r\nSupport a responsible party to develop the costing framework for the implementation of EVAW  legislation\r\n\r\nOrganize a consultation with media houses  and the Ministry of Information and Communication and Women Children and Social Welfare to discuss gender responsive media reporting\r\n\r\nSupport orientation workshops for media personnel on gender sensitive reporting on VAW/G and other critical women’s rights issues (discriminatory and harmful traditional practices) using the Right to Information Act\r\n\r\nSupport the MOWCSW to identify male leaders in consultation with women’s groups, CSAG and the Men Engage Alliance Nepal Group\r\n\r\nSupport the establishment of network of male leaders to promote the engagement of boys and men in VAW/G prevention and link network to the HeforShe Campaign"
      },
      "ne": null
